><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 27, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ndc1665702760212.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ndc1665702760212.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ndc1665702760212.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ndc1665702760212\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">occurrence \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__occurrence_305124\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface data type containing a single occurrence of an entity. For use in parameters.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__topic_d92747e1_d92748e1_d92749e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__p_d92750e1_d92751e1_d92752e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">params</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__p_d92753e1_d92754e1_d92755e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">occurrence</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">EntityName</var>{<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">.</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ModelName</var>} <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">:</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Direction</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__p_d92756e1_d92757e1_d92758e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endparams</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__topic_d61752e1_d61753e1_d61754e1_d61755e1_d61756e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d685127e94\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__p_d92762e1_d92763e1_d92764e1\">Use in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">params</span> blocks of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">operation</span> definitions to define the data type of a parameter.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__p_d92765e1_d92766e1_d92767e1\">Occurrence parameters cannot be used in entries and\n            functions (global or local ProcScript modules) and in global ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__topic_d61757e1_d61758e1_d61759e1_d61760e1_d61761e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d685127e112\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__p_d92771e1_d92772e1_d92773e1\">An occurrence parameter transfers the current occurrence of the specified entity from one component to another component.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"ndc1665702760212__note_w2598ab1b7b7b5_w2599ab1b7b7_w2600ab1b7_w2601ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Only fields\n               whose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Is External</span> property is <code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code> can be included in the occurrence parameter.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aco1665702561780.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Occurrences</a><p>An occurrence is the runtime instance of an entity. Although the entity determines the fields an occurrence may have, and some of its default properties and behavior, each occurrence is unique and contains one set of the fields, whether they contain data or not.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pta1665702586322.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Is External</a><p>Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tpe1665702530336.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>params…endparams</a><p>Declare the parameter block for an operation, function, or global ProcScript.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614757\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614757\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "occurrence Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 27, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 occurrence Uniface data type containing a single occurrence of an entity. For use in parameters. params occurrence EntityName { . ModelName } : Direction endparams Use Use in params blocks of operation definitions to define the data type of a parameter. Occurrence parameters cannot be used in entries and functions (global or local ProcScript modules) and in global ProcScript. Description An occurrence parameter transfers the current occurrence of the specified entity from one component to another component. Note: Only fields whose Is External property is T can be included in the occurrence parameter. Related Links Occurrences An occurrence is the runtime instance of an entity. Although the entity determines the fields an occurrence may have, and some of its default properties and behavior, each occurrence is unique and contains one set of the fields, whether they contain data or not. Is External Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter. params…endparams Declare the parameter block for an operation, function, or global ProcScript. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}